cars.description: This is an immaculate 2006 Nissan Rogue with only 25000 miles on it. Leather seats, power everything.
This is a 2009 Toyota 4Runner with only 5000 miles on it. Has other stuff thats really great.
This is a barely driveable 1972 Ford F-150 with only 150000 miles on it.
